{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"r5ee5da2e9ccswia2nes0fs","title":"Redis","desc":"","updated":1697425370049,"created":1697424929954,"custom":{},"fname":"system-design.Redis","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"222e1da639c93bcaac0e67d08ef323ba","links":[],"anchors":{"redis":{"type":"header","text":"Redis","value":"redis","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"redis-is-fast":{"type":"header","text":"Redis is fast","value":"redis-is-fast","line":12,"column":0,"depth":3},"caching":{"type":"header","text":"Caching","value":"caching","line":16,"column":0,"depth":3},"session-store":{"type":"header","text":"Session store","value":"session-store","line":22,"column":0,"depth":3}},"children":[],"parent":"ue4oml1si982t3mmbthyxi9","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"redis\">Redis<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#redis\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"redis-1\">Redis<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#redis-1\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.bytebytego.com/p/the-6-most-impactful-ways-redis-is\">https://blog.bytebytego.com/p/the-6-most-impactful-ways-redis-is</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"redis-is-fast\">Redis is fast<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#redis-is-fast\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>In-mem storage &#x26; Single threaded</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"caching\">Caching<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#caching\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Shortcut access to hot data (high frequent access)</li>\n<li>More complexity to manage cache coherence (\"is the uniformity of shared resource data that ends up stored in multiple local caches\")</li>\n<li>Tradeoff: Space vs time. Duplicate data -> faster access</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"session-store\">Session store<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#session-store\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Store session in redis instead of in app -> better for load rebalancing\n<ul>\n<li>No \"sticky-session\"</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Support expiration</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron","value":"dendron","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["u5a2e2vvfn3x7k0shuvmb1b","qw8y69zxn8wr7tzz4gtcrrv","q7qw45jglqwmynary64q67c","6wjqcjgkrpeqtmzb1o8o1q8","3ervbn5we7t8v2l2vwtx847","4qi2z0z9fquupbd651xausx","sencgim78q74o1zuyvy1vz7","ue4oml1si982t3mmbthyxi9","zrogwjgtze8ne5joqpz8ty9","oesia0lbzh03fsoy124ck0k","el3p9zjue6h3b6zsl9oejkt","t5grkmcwvu4nl43igsj4gxz"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"# Welcome to my page\n\n- This is a place where I write my knowledge in both Vietnamese and English.\n- Please feel free to correct me if there is anything not right.\n\n## Contacts\n\n- [Github](https://github.com/thanhpp)\n- [Discord](https://discord.gg/ugNRjFNqjp)\n- [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/thanhpp/)\n\n## Dendron\n\n- [Home Page](https://wiki.dendron.so/)"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"alwaysPrompt","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"vaults":[{